In regular octagon $ABCDEFGH$, $M$ and $N$ are midpoints of $\overline{BC}$ and $\overline{FG}$ respectively.  Compute $[ABMO]/[EDCMO]$. ($[ABCD]$ denotes the area of polygon $ABCD$.) [asy]
